<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>{dede:field.title/}_{dede:global.cfg_webname/}</title>
  <meta name="keywords" content="{dede:field name='keywords'/}" />
  <meta name="description" content="{dede:field name='description' function='html2text(@me)'/}" />
</head>
<body>
  <%-include ../../public/header.ejs%>
  <%-include ../../public/nbanner.ejs%>
  <%-include ../../public/search.ejs%>
  <%-include ../../public/breadcrumb.ejs%>
  <!-- 主框架 -->
  <div class="l-container clearfix">
    <!-- 左侧导航 -->
    <div class="l-leftnav">
      <h2 class="l-leftnav__title">正畸矫正</h2>
      <div class="l-leftnav__list">
        {dede:channelartlist typeid="1"}
        <div class="l-leftnav__item" data-id="{dede:field.id/}">
          <a class="l-leftnav__item__label" href="{dede:field.typeurl/}">{dede:field.typename/}</a>
          <div class="l-leftnav__item__children">
            {dede:channelarttlist}
            <a class="l-leftnav__item__children__item" href="{dede:field.typeurl/}" data-id="{dede:field.id/}">{dede:field.typename/}</a>
            {/dede:channelarttlist}
          </div>
        </div>
        {/dede:channelartlist}
      </div>
      <div class="l-leftnav__contact">
        <span>资讯热线</span>
        <p>{dede:global.tel_one/}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- 右侧容器 -->
    <div class="l-rightbody">
      <div class="l-rightbody__title">
        <span>{dede:field.typename/}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="l-product">
        <!-- 产品容器 -->
        <div class="l-product__wrapper clearfix">
          <!-- 产品图片 -->
          <div class="l-product__imgs">
            <ul class="l-product__imgs__list clearfix">
              {dede:productimagelist}
              <li class="l-product__imgs__item">
                <img src="[field:imgsrc/]" alt="[field:text/]"/>
              </li>
              {/dede:productimagelist}
            </ul>
            <div class="l-product__imgs__tab">
              <div class="l-product__imgs__tab__item l-product__imgs__tab__item--left prev"></div>
              <div class="l-product__imgs__tab__item l-product__imgs__tab__item--right next"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="l-product__imgs__page pageState">1/1</div>
          </div>
          <!-- 产品描述 -->
          <div class="l-product__main">
            <h2 class="l-product__title">产品名称</h2>
            <div class="l-product__info">
              {dede:field.sku/}
            </div>
            <div class="l-product__contact clearfix">
              <div class="l-product__contact__phone">
                <span>咨询热线</span>{dede:global.tel_one/}
              </div>
              <a type="button" target="__blank" href="http://wpa.qq.com/msgrd?v=3&uin={dede:gloabl.qq/}&site=qq&menu=yes" class="l-product__contact__btn">在线咨询</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 产品介绍 -->
        <div class="l-product__content">
          <div class="l-product__subtitle">产品介绍</div>
          <p>{dede:field.body/}</p>
        </div>
        <!-- 厂家承诺 -->
        <div class="l-product__content">
          <div class="l-product__subtitle">厂家承诺</div>
          <b>1.严谨的品质控制</b>
          <p>6道生产工序都必须经过82项厂内质检，检查、试验标准，合格后填写检验记录。打造客户满意的产品，对“零缺陷”持续追求。欧能对设备质量把关十分苛刻，严格的过程控制，只为打造更好的油温机，让客户在使用中得到更好的体验！</p>
          <b>2.超长的保修期限</b>
          <p>油温机整机质量保修一年，提供终身售后服务保障。 </p>
          <b>3.完善的售后服务</b>
          <p>服务宗旨：专业、快速、周到、准确 </p>
          <p>服务目标：服务质量达到客户满意。 </p>
          <p>服务效率：接到售后电话，技术售后人员将在3个小时内给客户详细的电话指导解决方案，如不能消除故障，24小时内准时抵达用户工厂并开始维修！</p>
          <form class="l-product__form" action="/mail/sendmail.php" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="demand" value="采购意向" />
            <div class="l-product__form__item">
              <span>联系人：</span>
              <input class="l-product__form__input" name="name" type="text">
            </div>
            <div class="l-product__form__item">
              <span>手机：</span>
              <input class="l-product__form__input" name="phone" type="text">
            </div>
            <div class="l-product__form__item">
              <span>公司名称：</span>
              <input class="l-product__form__input" name="company" type="text">
            </div>
            <div class="l-product__form__item">
              <span>邮箱：</span>
              <input class="l-product__form__input" name="email" type="text">
            </div>
            <div class="l-product__form__item">
              <span>采购意向：</span>
              <textarea class="l-product__form__textarea" name="message"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="l-product__form__btn-group">
              <button type="submit">提交</button>
              <button type="reset">重填</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <%-include ../../public/footer.ejs%>
  <script src="/templets/yiliao/static/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/templets/yiliao/static/supersilder.js"></script>
</html>